en_192124_0	Met Department says showers or thundershowers will occur at times in Western, Southern, Sabaragamuwa, Central and North-Western provinces and fairly heavy falls above 75 mm can be expected at some places.
en_192124_1	Showers or thundershowers may occur at few places in Uva province and in Batticaloa and Ampara districts after 2 pm.
en_192124_2	Light showers may occur at few places in Anuradhapura district.
en_192124_3	Fairly strong gusty winds up to 50kmph can be expected over Uva and Southern provinces.
